title: Don't try to collect data I would never need to use.
pid: 414195b8-4ef4-4195-82ef-bc44f4285ba2
body: |2-
  Data about when I wrote something is like this.
  To analyze that would be to navel-gaze. I won't.
  I don't have enough time for the first-order objects,
  which I care about understanding more than I care about
  pinning down my personal history of ideas.
